response.overview: Jamie Mosberg's explosive 2002 surf film produced by Billabong, featuring an all-star lineup of the brand's legendary team riders.  This 42-minute surf film showcases the incredible talent of Billabong's roster including Joel Parkinson, Taj Burrow, Shane Dorian, Mark Occhilupo (Occy), Benji Weatherly, and many more of the early 2000s' best surfers. - https://nalu.tv/collections/surfing-films/products/feeding-freenzy-stream
response.title: Feeding Frenzy
